<template>
    <a-table :dataSource="dataSource" :columns="columns" />
  </template>
  
  <script>
    export default {
      setup() {
        return {
          dataSource: [
            {
              key: '1',
              name: 'bob',
              age: 32,
              address: '西湖区湖底公园1号',
            },
            {
              key: '2',
              name: '胡彦祖',
              age: 42,
              address: '西湖区湖底公园1号',
            },
          ],
  
          columns: [
            {
              title: '姓名',
              dataIndex: 'name',
              key: 'name',
            },
            {
              title: '年龄',
              dataIndex: 'age',
              key: 'age',
            },
            {
              title: '住址',
              dataIndex: 'address',
              key: 'address',
            },
          ],
        };
      },
    };
  </script>
